{"article_id":"gLsGR3KU64bZWgFq","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The agreement is an acknowledgement by the Ted Cruz and John Kasich campaigns","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that neither candidate can overtake Donald Trump before the convention ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"but that they can still deny him a first-ballot victory .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"|","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"AP Photo","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Cruz and Kasich team up","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"to stop Trump","depth":3},{"id":7,"text":"Ted Cruz and John Kasich have begun coordinating their campaign strategy","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"to stop Donald Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"an abrupt alliance","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"announced Sunday night","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that includes Kasich quitting his efforts in Indiana","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"and Cruz clearing a path for the Ohio governor in Oregon and New Mexico .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"\" To ensure","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"that we nominate a Republican","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"who can unify the Republican Party","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"and win in November ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"our campaign will focus its time and resources in Indiana","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"and in turn clear the path for Gov . Kasich","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"to compete in Oregon and New Mexico ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and we would hope","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that allies of both campaigns would follow our lead , \"","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Cruz campaign manager Jeff Roe said in a statement .","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"Trump fired back late Sunday on Twitter ,","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"writing ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"\" Wow , just announced","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"that Lyin ' Ted and Kasich are going to collude","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"in order to keep me from getting the Republican nomination .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"DESPERATION ! \"","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"He added , for good measure :","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"\" Lyin ' Ted and Kasich are mathematically dead and totally desperate .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Their donors & special interest groups are not happy with them .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Sad ! \"","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Trump followed up early Monday morning with a lengthier statement","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"released by his campaign ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"calling out both rivals","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"for reverting to `` collusion ''","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"to stop him .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"`` When two candidates","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"who have no path to victory","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"get together","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"to stop a candidate","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"who is expanding the party by millions of voters ,","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"( all of whom will drop out","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"if I am not in the race )","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"it is yet another example of everything","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"that is wrong in Washington and our political system , ''","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"`` This horrible act of desperation , from two campaigns","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"who have totally failed ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"makes me even more determined , for the good of the Republican Party and our country , to prevail ! ''","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"The new Cruz-Kasich pact is an acknowledgment","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"that neither man can overtake Trump in the race ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"and both know","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"their best shot","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"at preventing Trump from clinching the nomination outright","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"is to team up","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"to block his path","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"and force a contested convention .","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"And it may still be too late :","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Trump is closing in on the number of delegates","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"he needs","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"to win the nomination .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"The deal also highlights the urgency","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"the anti-Trump forces feel in Indiana ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"where a strong Cruz performance in the May 3 primary could deny the Manhattan billionaire 57 of the delegates","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"he needs","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"to reach a majority","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"before the Republican National Convention convenes in July .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"For now , Trump leads in the RealClearPolitics average of Indiana polls by 6.3 percentage points .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Cruz is competing hard , however ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"and supportive super PACs had plans","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"to spend more than $ 1 million there in an ad buy","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"that included an anti-Kasich spot .","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"The move allows Kasich to focus on two smaller-market states","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"where his limited campaign cash might have greater impact","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"than it would in Indiana .","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"Kasich ended March with barely more than $ 1 million on hand .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"But it puts Indiana ' s handful of pro-Kasich delegates in an awkward spot :","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"defending a decision","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"to back a candidate","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"who is intentionally forfeiting their state .","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"Kasich ' s field offices in Indiana are expected to shutter this week ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"and he canceled his remaning events there .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Tom John , one of those pro-Kasich delegates and a local GOP leader in Indiana , said","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"he has no qualms supporting Kasich at a contested convention","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"despite the strategy shift .","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"\" This strikes me as a choice","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"made","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"based on the limited campaign time ,","depth":15},{"id":90,"text":"and so it made sense for both campaigns to do this , \"","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"\" Who I support","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"is still about the best Republican option for the fall election . \"","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"Previously , the Cruz campaign had largely refused to acknowledge the Ohio governor ' s presence in the race","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"except to dismiss him as a spoiler ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"and had insisted","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"that only a two-man race between Cruz and Trump would halt the real estate mogul ' s momentum .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"\" Who ? \"","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Roe replied last week ,","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"when asked by reporters about Kasich .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"The Cruz campaign had also previously planned to compete in those states , especially in New Mexico ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"with a memo from the campaign last month saying","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"data showed","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"that Cruz could win a majority of that state ' s delegates .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Also Sunday , Kasich chief strategist John Weaver announced ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"\" We will shift our campaign ' s resources West","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"and give the Cruz campaign a clear path in Indiana . \"","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"\" In turn , we will focus our time and resources in New Mexico and Oregon , both areas","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"that are structurally similar to the Northeast politically ,","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"where Gov . Kasich is performing well , \"","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"Weaver wrote .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"\" We would expect independent third-party groups to do the same","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"and honor the commitments","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"made by the Cruz and Kasich campaigns . \"","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Cruz is well ahead of Kasich in the delegate count ,","depth":3},{"id":116,"text":"but both currently lag well behind Trump","depth":5},{"id":117,"text":"and have acknowledged","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"that at this point their best shot","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"at beating him","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"would come at a contested convention .","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"\" Our goal is to have an open convention in Cleveland ,","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"where we are confident","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"a candidate","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"capable of uniting the party","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"and winning in November","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"will emerge as the nominee , \"","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"Weaver said in the statement .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":255,"left":134,"right":254,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":134,"left":132,"right":133,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":132,"left":130,"right":131,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":0,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":131,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":241,"right":253,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":149,"right":240,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":139,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":135,"right":138,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":135,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"lef